It is a "multi-tenant document analysis  project".
Multi-tenant architecture is a software design where a single instance of an application serves multiple customers (tenants), ensuring data isolation and security.

Tech-Stack :-
1. Multi-Tenant = Architecture or Isolated data per organization
2. Next.js 16 = App router with server components & layouts
3. PostgreSQL + Prisma = Type-safe database with multi-tenant schema
4. Clerk = Authentication & organisation management
5. Google Gemini AI = Document summarization, sentiment analysis & entity extraction
6. Shadcn/UI + Tailwind = Modern & fast user-interface
7. Vercel Blob = Secure document storage

React-Markdown --> Used for formating of AI response